{"tid":1677651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"許立燊話唔選又選，突空降 狙擊陳天俊兩父子界票","createTime":"2019-10-27T08:41:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T12:56:05.000Z","uid":245250,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"f8c87f6a364781cac9f1750f2a686f9e63b92d8e","tid":1677651,"uid":245250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T08:41:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1068161\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1068161&d=HXPWCXSY8fSkht0R8v8uOcLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=89d36267\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1068161&h=edf626be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1068161</a><br />\n<br />\n沙田錦濤區民主派內訌 許立燊原本參選耀安區 被指「反口」參選<br />\n<br />\n沙田「錦濤」選區有四人參選，其中兩人屬民主派，包括現任區議員陳國強之子陳天俊，及早前稱不會與民主派「撞區」的許立燊。<br />\n<br />\n陳國強亦一度報名參選，但於遞交提名兩日後退選。陳國強表示一直有意連任，惟因官司纏身最後決定退選，但指許立燊一直都沒有聯絡他，「選唔選唔緊要，但唔好講咗唔會選又選」，認為許不道德。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳天俊又表示，自己作為錦濤區居民，完全沒有看見許立燊進行地區工作，質疑許立燊「服務咗耀安咁多年」， 因與另一名民主派撞區而選擇退出該區，現時卻又「空降」錦濤選區，與民主派參選人「內訌」。為免建制派享「漁人得利」，陳天俊希望舉辦初選，但認為應該將門檻提升，至少要有10%當區選民投票，以提高代表性，並舉辦選舉論壇讓選民知悉雙方理念，惟他獲悉許立燊以涉及選舉開支為由，拒絕出席選舉論壇。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h7SKmBM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh7SKmBM.jpg&h=4859ab9a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P5XBW97.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP5XBW97.jpg&h=8ae21c79&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j3mK53t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj3mK53t.jpg&h=430fb9c7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t80WW99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft80WW99.jpg&h=fd73eb89&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sgKQhaa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsgKQhaa.jpg&h=dd989e1c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9zacvva.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9zacvva.jpg&h=cefb2a75&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ct0WXab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fct0WXab.jpg&h=e9f60206&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1bRjavb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1bRjavb.jpg&h=40a106f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7afa1fc61e61678c21b61d01225a27d80420025","tid":1677651,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T08:41:52.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"522d099b2a5138cd1fb123dcaff3b63e56a7d73d","tid":1677651,"uid":245250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T08:45:32.000Z","msg":"許立燊出爾反爾 突空降錦濤區<br />\n<br />\n許立燊受訪時指出，他之前在耀安選區進行地區工作，但有另一民主派團隊有意參選，為免有利建制派當選，他選擇退出該區，其後繼續在馬鞍山服務市民。他強調現時未決定參選哪一區，惟絕對不會與民主派「撞區」，但如有任何意外，他可能會作為後備，補充民主派陣營。"},{"pid":"f4b27cf2a3cca97208c828b9718440b259a40bcd","tid":1677651,"uid":236676,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T09:32:34.000Z","msg":"支持陳天俊"},{"pid":"556623bb25ddd611f019d1927bd20a55dc0be699","tid":1677651,"uid":62714,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T09:34:46.000Z","msg":"屌你老母呢個時勢仲內鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be5606f7717165c23dfb030b3be0f52f715faf81","tid":1677651,"uid":32051,"like":10,"dislike":4,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T12:02:01.000Z","msg":"許立燊，屌你老母呀<br />\n返去屌你師傅麥傻鳩個屎眼啦"},{"pid":"8b7d18ca075971008d134128ce9a64be23240ca4","tid":1677651,"uid":75082,"like":9,"dislike":22,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T13:03:34.000Z","msg":"陳國強驚dq<br />\n然後做個假象被飯民迫害<br />\n個仔一入到閘就即刻退選<br />\n真係當所有人係on9<br />\n嫖書嫖到懵撚咗牙強哥<br />\n自認本土派玩帝制世襲？<br />\n仆街死啦去<br />\n仲推條o靚邱文勁去搞鳩鐘禮謙果區， 搞到好大機會兩區都仆晒街， 屌佢老味啦陳國強<br />\n帝制世襲冚家剷，一票不投陳天俊<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72729d93da5522afa6bc2b5b076fe612956190cf","tid":1677651,"uid":75082,"like":6,"dislike":15,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"be5606f7717165c23dfb030b3be0f52f715faf81","tid":1677651,"uid":32051,"like":10,"dislike":4,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T12:02:01.000Z","msg":"許立燊，屌你老母呀<br />\n返去屌你師傅麥傻鳩個屎眼啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T13:11:01.000Z","msg":"惡撚到呢<br />\n一定要俾你地兩父子玩帝制世襲其他人都唔準選？ <br />\n仆街啦去"},{"pid":"037feb63e360e3de857ad4800971213eaaa071a2","tid":1677651,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T13:13:40.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，借個位<br />\n鐘庭耀發起全港性民調，追蹤長期民意<br />\n<br />\n連登post: 鍾庭耀教授都企左出來....你仲做冷氣軍師??<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n眾籌link: <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209%2F&d=HXPWCXSY8fSkht0R8v8uOcLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=3137b452\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/</a>"},{"pid":"a358a695ff93ba9c987e2786e36ca84528aac078","tid":1677651,"uid":192409,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T13:15:01.000Z","msg":"陳國強係撚民主派"},{"pid":"4e362832034404787faf48a669496d9ec8d47412","tid":1677651,"uid":75082,"like":5,"dislike":9,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T13:18:50.000Z","msg":"陳國強一直攻擊民主派, 咁民主派唔當你係同路人好合理呀<br />\n又要比你攻擊, 又要讓位比你帝制世襲呀? 有無咁著數呀on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"